{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><br>A free-to-play turn based RPG that serves as a short demo.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The main story is a short series of quests to help Anri recover an artifact.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Meet interesting people.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Recruit new party members.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Learn about your party members and the region you are exploring.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore the world and fight challenging turn-based battles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Repeatable dungeons with harvesting and chest nodes that reset.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play fun mini games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gather food and cook it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Designed with widescreen monitors and laptops in mind</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In addition to the base game, we have the following DLCs available:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Optimization DLCs: a free download for Luminous Skies: A Short Adventure and one for Interstellar and it is intended to be used on lower end operating systems. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  The other DLCs are are effectively 2 games and 1 big expansion pack in a trench coat. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Luminous Skies: The Pilgrimage: A standalone game set prior to the events in A Short Adventure and Horizons.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Luminous Skies: Horizons: an add-on for A Short Adventure. It adds a many new quests, new encounters, new overworld zones, secrets, weapons and armors, and new party members. We hope to add additional content on a regular basis. Mainland and new world access has opened up for more exploration. If The Pilgrimage is a standalone game, Horizons is a standalone expansion pack.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Luminous Skies: Interstellar. Another standalone game, this time set in a Sci-Fi setting. Explore many worlds and contend with the Solar Regime and their plots to conquer all of known space.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Please refer to our announcements in the community section for further details on updates.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">What are you waiting for? It's all out there for you to find and experience for yourself.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2384140/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1731104580","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2384140/page.bg.jpg?t=1731104580","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2384140/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1731104580","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2384140/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1731104580","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><br>A free-to-play turn based RPG that serves as a short demo.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The main story is a short series of quests to help Anri recover an artifact.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Meet interesting people.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Recruit new party members.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Learn about your party members and the region you are exploring.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore the world and fight challenging turn-based battles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Repeatable dungeons with harvesting and chest nodes that reset.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play fun mini games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gather food and cook it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Designed with widescreen monitors and laptops in mind</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In addition to the base game, we have the following DLCs available:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Optimization DLCs: a free download for Luminous Skies: A Short Adventure and one for Interstellar and it is intended to be used on lower end operating systems. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  The other DLCs are are effectively 2 games and 1 big expansion pack in a trench coat. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Luminous Skies: The Pilgrimage: A standalone game set prior to the events in A Short Adventure and Horizons.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Luminous Skies: Horizons: an add-on for A Short Adventure. It adds a many new quests, new encounters, new overworld zones, secrets, weapons and armors, and new party members. We hope to add additional content on a regular basis. Mainland and new world access has opened up for more exploration. If The Pilgrimage is a standalone game, Horizons is a standalone expansion pack.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Luminous Skies: Interstellar. Another standalone game, this time set in a Sci-Fi setting. Explore many worlds and contend with the Solar Regime and their plots to conquer all of known space.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Please refer to our announcements in the community section for further details on updates.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">What are you waiting for? It's all out there for you to find and experience for yourself.</p>","developers":["Al_Kovac"],"dlc":[2384220,2384221,2384222,2840850,2892120],"genres":[{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"RPG","id":"3"},{"description":"Free To Play","id":"37"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2384140/header.jpg?t=1731104580","is_free":true,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":256939327,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256939327/movie480.mp4?t=168692218